{"id":831,"parent_id":828,"book_id":1,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":831,"title":"Ezekiel 3","subtitle":"","short_title":"Ezek.","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/3","content":[["div",[".titleNumber","Chapter 3"],[".studySummary",["i","Ezekiel is made a watchman unto the house of Israel—The blood of Israel is required at his hand unless he raises the warning voice."]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/3.1","order":"02.27.003.55085"},["b","1"],"Moreover he said unto me, Son of man, eat that thou findest; eat this",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_1a"},"roll"],", and go speak unto the house of Israel."],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/3.2","order":"02.27.003.55086"},["b","2"],"So I opened my mouth, and he caused me to eat that roll."],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/3.3","order":"02.27.003.55087"},["b","3"],"And he said unto me, Son of man, cause thy belly to eat, and fill thy bowels with this roll that I give thee. Then did I",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_3a"},"eat"],["i","it;"],"and it was in my mouth as honey for sweetness."],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/3.4","order":"02.27.003.55088"},["b","4"],"¶And he said unto me, Son of man, go, get thee unto the house of Israel, and speak with my words unto them."],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/3.5","order":"02.27.003.55089"},["b","5"],"For thou",["i","art"],"not sent to a people of a strange speech and of an hard language,",["i","but"],"to the house of Israel;"],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/3.6","order":"02.27.003.55090"},["b","6"],"Not to many people of a strange speech and of an hard language, whose words thou canst not understand. Surely, had I sent thee to them, they would have",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_6a"},"hearkened"],"unto thee."],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/3.7","order":"02.27.003.55091"},["b","7"],"But the house of Israel will not hearken unto thee; for they will not hearken unto me: for all the house of Israel",["i","are"],"impudent and",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_7a"},"hardhearted"],"."],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/3.8","order":"02.27.003.55092"},["b","8"],"Behold, I have made thy face strong against their faces, and thy forehead strong against their foreheads."],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/3.9","order":"02.27.003.55093"},["b","9"],"As an",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_9a"},"adamant"],"harder than flint have I made thy forehead: fear them not, neither be dismayed at their looks, though they",["i","be"],"a rebellious house."],["div",{"id":"10","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/3.10","order":"02.27.003.55094"},["b","10"],"Moreover he said unto me, Son of man, all my words that I shall speak unto thee receive in thine heart, and hear with thine ears."],["div",{"id":"11","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/3.11","order":"02.27.003.55095"},["b","11"],"And go, get thee to them of the captivity, unto the children of thy people, and speak unto them, and tell them, Thus saith",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_11a"},"the Lord",["span.smallCaps","God"]],"; whether they will hear, or whether they will forbear."],["div",{"id":"12","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/3.12","order":"02.27.003.55096"},["b","12"],"Then the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_12a"},"spirit"],"took me up, and I heard behind me a voice of a great rushing,",["i","saying,"],"Blessed",["i","be"],"the glory of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"from his place."],["div",{"id":"13","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/3.13","order":"02.27.003.55097"},["b","13"],["i","I heard"],"also the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_13a"},"noise"],"of the wings of the living creatures that touched one another, and the noise of the wheels over against them, and a noise of a great rushing."],["div",{"id":"14","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/3.14","order":"02.27.003.55098"},["b","14"],"So the spirit lifted me up, and took me away, and I went in bitterness, in the heat of my spirit; but the hand of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"was strong upon me."],["div",{"id":"15","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/3.15","order":"02.27.003.55099"},["b","15"],"¶Then I came to them of the captivity at Tel-abib, that dwelt by the river of Chebar, and I sat where they sat, and remained there astonished among them seven days."],["div",{"id":"16","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/3.16","order":"02.27.003.55100"},["b","16"],"And it came to pass at the end of seven days, that the word of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"came unto me, saying,"],["div",{"id":"17","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/3.17","order":"02.27.003.55101"},["b","17"],"Son of man, I have made thee a",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_17a"},"watchman"],"unto the house of Israel: therefore hear the word at my mouth, and give them",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_17b"},"warning"],"from me."],["div",{"id":"18","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/3.18","order":"02.27.003.55102"},["b","18"],"When I say unto the wicked, Thou shalt surely",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_18a"},"die"],"; and thou givest him not",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_18b"},"warning"],", nor speakest to warn the wicked from his wicked way, to save his life; the same wicked",["i","man"],"shall",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_18c"},"die"],"in his",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_18d"},"iniquity"],"; but his blood will I",["sup","e"],["a",{"href":"fn_18e"},"require"],"at thine hand."],["div",{"id":"19","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/3.19","order":"02.27.003.55103"},["b","19"],"Yet if thou",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_19a"},"warn"],"the wicked, and he turn not from his wickedness, nor from his wicked way, he shall die in his iniquity; but thou hast delivered thy soul."],["div",{"id":"20","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/3.20","order":"02.27.003.55104"},["b","20"],"Again, When a",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_20a"},"righteous"],["i","man"],"doth",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_20b"},"turn"],"from his",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_20c"},"righteousness"],", and commit iniquity, and I lay a",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_20d"},"stumblingblock"],"before him, he shall die: because thou hast not given him warning, he shall die in his sin, and his righteousness which he hath done shall not be remembered; but his blood will I require at thine hand."],["div",{"id":"21","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/3.21","order":"02.27.003.55105"},["b","21"],"Nevertheless if thou warn the righteous",["i","man,"],"that the righteous sin not, and he doth not sin, he shall surely live, because he is",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_21a"},"warned"],"; also thou hast delivered thy soul."],["div",{"id":"22","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/3.22","order":"02.27.003.55106"},["b","22"],"¶And the hand of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"was there upon me; and he said unto me, Arise, go forth into the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_22a"},"plain"],", and I will there talk with thee."],["div",{"id":"23","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/3.23","order":"02.27.003.55107"},["b","23"],"Then I arose, and went forth into the plain: and, behold, the glory of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"stood there, as the glory which I saw by the river of Chebar: and I",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_23a"},"fell"],"on my face."],["div",{"id":"24","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/3.24","order":"02.27.003.55108"},["b","24"],"Then the spirit entered into me, and set me upon my feet, and spake with me, and said unto me, Go, shut thyself within thine house."],["div",{"id":"25","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/3.25","order":"02.27.003.55109"},["b","25"],"But thou, O son of man, behold, they shall put bands upon thee, and shall bind thee with them, and thou shalt not go out among them:"],["div",{"id":"26","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/3.26","order":"02.27.003.55110"},["b","26"],"And I will make thy tongue cleave to the roof of thy mouth, that thou shalt be",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_26a"},"dumb"],", and shalt not be to them a reprover: for they",["i","are"],"a rebellious house."],["div",{"id":"27","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/3.27","order":"02.27.003.55111"},["b","27"],"But when I speak with thee, I will open thy",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_27a"},"mouth"],", and thou shalt say unto them, Thus",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_27b"},"saith"],"the Lord",["span.smallCaps","God"],"; He that heareth, let him hear; and he that forbeareth, let him forbear: for they",["i","are"],"a rebellious house."]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"1a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/3.1a","order":"02.27.003.55112"},["b","1a"],["span.small","HEB"],"scroll."],["div",{"id":"3a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/3.3a","order":"02.27.003.55114"},["b","3a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jer/15.16"},"Jer. 15:16"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/2.8"},"Ezek. 2:8"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/rev/10.10.9-10"},"Rev. 10:10 (9–10)"],"."],["div",{"id":"6a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/3.6a","order":"02.27.003.55116"},["b","6a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/matt/11.21.21,23"},"Matt. 11:21 (21, 23)"],"."],["div",{"id":"7a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/3.7a","order":"02.27.003.55118"},["b","7a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/hardheartedness"},"TG Hardheartedness"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/stubbornness"},"Stubbornness"],"."],["div",{"id":"9a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/3.9a","order":"02.27.003.55120"},["b","9a"],["span.small","OR"],"diamond."],["div",{"id":"11a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/3.11a","order":"02.27.003.55122"},["b","11a"],["span.small","HEB"],"the Lord Jehovah."],["div",{"id":"12a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/3.12a","order":"02.27.003.55124"},["b","12a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/god-spirit-of"},"TG God, Spirit of"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/guidance-divine"},"Guidance, Divine"],"."],["div",{"id":"13a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/3.13a","order":"02.27.003.55126"},["b","13a"],["span.small","OR"],"sound."],["div",{"id":"17a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/3.17a","order":"02.27.003.55128"},["b","17a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/delegation-of-responsibility"},"TG Delegation of Responsibility"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/watchman"},"Watchman"],"."],["div",{"id":"17b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/3.17b","order":"02.27.003.55130"},["b","17b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/priesthood-magnifying-callings-within"},"TG Priesthood, Magnifying Callings within"],"."],["div",{"id":"18a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/3.18a","order":"02.27.003.55132"},["b","18a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/33.14"},"Ezek. 33:14"],"."],["div",{"id":"18b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/3.18b","order":"02.27.003.55134"},["b","18b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/watch"},"TG Watch"],"."],["div",{"id":"18c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/3.18c","order":"02.27.003.55136"},["b","18c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/justice"},"TG Justice"],"."],["div",{"id":"18d","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/3.18d","order":"02.27.003.55138"},["b","18d"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/sin"},"TG Sin"],"."],["div",{"id":"18e","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/3.18e","order":"02.27.003.55140"},["b","18e"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/accountability"},"TG Accountability"],"."],["div",{"id":"19a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/3.19a","order":"02.27.003.55142"},["b","19a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/prophets-mission-of"},"TG Prophets, Mission of"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/warn"},"Warn"],"."],["div",{"id":"20a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/3.20a","order":"02.27.003.55144"},["b","20a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/18.24"},"Ezek. 18:24"],"."],["div",{"id":"20b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/3.20b","order":"02.27.003.55146"},["b","20b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/33.12.12-13,18"},"Ezek. 33:12 (12–13, 18)"],"."],["div",{"id":"20c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/3.20c","order":"02.27.003.55148"},["b","20c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/righteousness"},"TG Righteousness"],"."],["div",{"id":"20d","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/3.20d","order":"02.27.003.55150"},["b","20d"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jer/6.21"},"Jer. 6:21"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/14.4.3-7"},"Ezek. 14:4 (3–7)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/26.20"},"2 Ne. 26:20"],"."],["div",{"id":"21a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/3.21a","order":"02.27.003.55152"},["b","21a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/1.4"},"D&C 1:4"],"."],["div",{"id":"22a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/3.22a","order":"02.27.003.55154"},["b","22a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/8.4"},"Ezek. 8:4"],"."],["div",{"id":"23a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/3.23a","order":"02.27.003.55156"},["b","23a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/1.28"},"Ezek. 1:28"],"."],["div",{"id":"26a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/3.26a","order":"02.27.003.55158"},["b","26a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/24.27"},"Ezek. 24:27"],"."],["div",{"id":"27a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/3.27a","order":"02.27.003.55160"},["b","27a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/prophecy"},"TG Prophecy"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/teaching-with-the-spirit"},"Teaching with the Spirit"],"."],["div",{"id":"27b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/3.27b","order":"02.27.003.55162"},["b","27b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/prophets-mission-of"},"TG Prophets, Mission of"],"."]]}
